Package oshi.jna.platform.mac

Interface IOKit

All Superinterfaces:
com.sun.jna.Library
public interface IOKit
extends com.sun.jna.Library
Power Supply stats. This class should be considered non-API as it may be removed if/when its code is incorporated into the JNA project.
Author:
widdis[at]gmail[dot]com
